9
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:37,160
That's true.

10
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:41,740
Anyone entering the conference room would have to pass through the hall,

11
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:44,560
and we've had people coming and going these past few days.

12
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,420
If someone had entered the villa,

13
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,039
we would have noticed.

14
