20
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,400
Gong Sun He,

21
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,760
stop keeping us in suspense.

22
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,620
Tell us who the killer is quickly.

23
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,560
Qing Tian.

24
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,120
What?

25
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:18,840
Are you suspecting me?

26
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,840
No,

27
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,200
I want to ask you,

28
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:25,600
